        public static final List<String> KNOWN_PROTOCOLS

        public URL(String urlString)
    throws MalformedURLException
        Create an instance of URL from urlString.
        Parameters:
        urlString - The string to create an URL from.
        Throws:
        MalformedURLException - This can occur if urlString does not match the pattern protocol://host[:port]/path, an unknown protocol is specified, or port is negative.
